Holotype MEXICO • ♀ (preserved in alcohol); Sinaloa State , Mazatlán , Urías coastal system, stn 2 (see also Gómez 2020a: 43 , fig. 1); 23.1587° N , 106.3326° W ; 1.8 m depth ;
